parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the TCM can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to sudden loss of power, difficulty shifting gears, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The "Transmission Malfunction" message appears on the instrument panel
the vehicle stalls or hesitates while driving
difficulty shifting gears
and the transmission slips or bucks.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the transmission to malfunction, leading to sudden loss of power, difficulty shifting gears, and potentially causing accidents.
symptoms: The vehicle jerks or shudders when shifting gears
the clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
and the vehicle has difficulty accelerating or decelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission system can cause the vehicle to stall or lose power, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The vehicle stalls or hesitates while driving
difficulty shifting gears
the transmission slips or bucks
and the vehicle has difficulty accelerating or decelerating.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the door to open while the vehicle is in motion, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door will not shut or latch
the door opens while the vehicle is in motion
the door latch is weak or broken
the door latch does not engage properly
the door latch is stuck
the door will not stay closed.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to hesitate, jerk, or shut off, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission shudders
hesitates
or jerks when accelerating
difficulty shifting gears
the vehicle slows down or shuts off without warning
the transmission light comes on
and the vehicle accelerates slowly or erratically.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the door latch can cause the door to open while driving, leading to accidents or injuries.
symptoms: The door will not shut or latch
the door opens while driving
the door latch is broken
and the door pops open while in motion.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the clutch can cause the vehicle to jerk or hesitate, leading to accidents or leaving the driver stranded.
symptoms: The clutch pedal feels soft or spongy
the clutch pedal sticks to the floor
the clutch pedal does not return to its normal position
and the vehicle jerks or hesitates when shifting gears.
